              dispersion error for all \$\$0 {\textbackslash}le {\textbackslash}
              alpha {\textbackslash}le 1\$\$. Moreover, for \$\${\textbackslash}
              alpha {\textbackslash}ne 0\$\$, the method can attenuate the
              spurious high-frequency components from the velocity and
              displacement fields.},
